description:
If you're looking for a fun way to celebrate Christmas, then join us for The First Noel "Karaoke"! It's just like regular karaoke, but with a twist—every song is sung in honour of Christmas!
Whether you're a first-time participant or a seasoned karaoke enthusiast, this event is sure to be a lot of fun.
